E-05 USER PART NO ISN'T INPUT
E-06 PRODUCTION ORDER DATE ISN'T INPUT
E-07 QUANTITY ISN'T INPUT
E-08 DELIVERY DATE ISN'T INPUT
E-09 IT IS MORE THAN 10 OR ORDER RECEIPT COUNT ISN'T INPUT
