E-19 THOUGH THERE IS NOT PROCESS, A DATE IS INPUT
E-20 THERE IS PROCESS, BUT THERE IS NOT A DATE
E-21 SHIP ORDER DAY IS EARLIER THAN THE PRODUCTION START DAY
E-22 DELIVERY DATE IS EARLIER THAN THE PROD ORDER DATE
